
<%# Head / Meta Data %>
<% title("Start Your Pilot Career | SimpliFly Flight School") %>
<% meta_description(" Join the team of instructors at Simplifly in Mesa, Phoenix, Scottsdale. Share your passion for aviation and inspire future pilots as an instructor. Apply now.") %>
<% meta_keywords("Flight Instructor Position, CFI Job, Instruct at Simplifly, Mesa Flight School, Phoenix Flight School, Scottsdale Flight School") %>

<%= render "shared/header"%>


<header
  class="relative top-0 lg:h-screen flex flex-col items-center justify-center"
>
    <!-- bg-overlay to darken -->
    <div class="hidden lg:block absolute w-full h-screen overflow-hidden">
        <%= image_tag "simplifly-sunset-gilbert-cfi-training.webp" , alt: "Sunset over Gilbert Arizona during CFI CFII training at Falcon Field SimpliFly Flight School", class: "h-full w-full object-cover object-center lg:object-top brightness-75 opacity-80"%>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row lg:px-5 z-10">
      
      <!-- Text -->
      <div class="text-white flex flex-col items-start pt-10 lg:pt-0 px-5 h-auto lg:w-1/2">
        <h1 class="text-3xl lg:text-7xl text-sky-400 font-header uppercase font-semibold">
          30 Day Accelerated <br class="hidden lg:block"> CFI & CFII Course
        </h1>
        <h2 class="text-lg lg:text-3xl text-white font-medium italic mt-3 hidden lg:block">
          Become a certified flight instructor.   <br class="hidden lg:block">
          Gain necessary flight time and experience.   <br class="hidden lg:block">
          Train the next generation of aviators. <br class="hidden lg:block">
        </h2>
      </div>

      <%# Form %>
      <div class="lg:w-1/2 mx-auto lg:rounded-2xl lg:border-2 lg:border-custom-50 bg-white py-5">
        <div class="px-5">
          <%= turbo_frame_tag 'form-section', class: "h-full" do %>
            <%= render "form", accel_cfi: @accel_cfi %>  
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
</header>

<section class="bg-gradient-to-b from-slate-50 to-sky-200 flex flex-col items-center">
  <div class="max-w-4xl flex flex-col pt-10 px-5">
    <h3 class="text-5xl font-header uppercase font-semibold">Get Started on Your Pilot Career</h3>
    <h4 class="text-3xl text-slate-600 italic py-5">Become a CFI/CFII in 30 days!</h4>
    <p class="text-lg">Join SimpliFly's accelerated CFI/CFII program and become a certified flight instructor in just 30 days! With small class sizes and a personalized training approach, you'll gain the skills and experience needed to start your aviation career quickly. Our program boasts a 100% pass rate and is designed for aspiring pilots ready to take the next step, whether you're building hours or looking for your first paid flying job. Get started today and become a confident, certified instructor!</p>
    
    <h3 class="text-5xl font-header uppercase font-semibold pt-20 pb-5">How Long Will it Take?</h3>
    <p class="text-lg">Becoming a flight instructor depends on meeting certain requirements, including a commercial pilot license and instrument rating, with at least 250 flight hours. Once those requirements are met, training can be completed in as little as a week for full-time students or over a few months for part-time learners.</p>

    <p class="text-lg pt-10">Our Accelerated CFI/CFII program is designed to get you certified in just 30 days, with new classes starting every month.  If you are accepted into the program, you will be paired with an instructor and be surrounded with peers that are focused on the same goal you are: becoming a certified flight instructor.</p>

    <h3 class="text-5xl font-header uppercase font-semibold pt-20 pb-5">What are the Eligibility Requirements?</h3>
    <ul class="list-disc text-lg pl-10 lg:pl-16">
      <li>Be 18 years of age</li>
      <li>Read, speak, write and understand the English language</li>
      <li>Hold a commercial pilot certificate and an instrument rating</li>
      <li>Have logged at least 250 hours of flight time</li>
      <li>Hold a valid FAA 3rd Class Medical Cerificate (or higher)</li>
      <li>Receive a logbook endorsement from an authorized instructor on the fundamentals of instructing</li>
      <li>Pass a knowledge test on the aeronautical knowledge areas appropriate to the flight instructor rating sought</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="text-slate-600 italic pt-5">Reference 14 CFR §61.183 for the entire list of eligibility requirements.</p>

    <h3 class="text-5xl font-header uppercase font-semibold pt-20 pb-5">The SimpliFly Guarantee</h3>
    <p class="text-lg pb-20">If you have completed your <%= link_to "private", private_pilot_path, class: "text-sky-600 hover:underline", data: {turbo: false}%>, <%= link_to "instrument", instrument_path, class: "text-sky-600 hover:underline", data: {turbo: false}%>, <%= link_to "commercial", commercial_path, class: "text-sky-600 hover:underline", data: {turbo: false}%>, and CFI training at SimpliFly, we have an exciting opportunity for you. As a testament to our confidence in your abilities, we offer a guaranteed interview for a teaching position as a CFI within our flight school. This exclusive opportunity allows you to showcase the knowledge and skills you have acquired during your training journey with us. Join our team of dedicated instructors, inspire future aviators, and make a meaningful impact in the aviation community. Take the next step in your career as a CFI with SimpliFly and let your passion for aviation soar.</p>
  </div>
</section>

